data.description: Beautiful expanded Heather Model in a vibrant, active, adult community. Enjoy resort-style amenities, 3 golf courses, fitness centers, tennis and performing arts theater. Hilton Head beaches are a short drive away! 2BR/2 BA, Den, Carolina Room and Screened-in Porch with private wooded view. Eat-in Kitchen with stainless steel appliances, gas range, tile backsplash and wood floors. Finished, heated and cooled garage with full screen door and 4 ft. extension. 1,550 sq. ft. Meticulously cared for and move in ready!
